<div class="content" name="WKSTA_INFO_1018" uuid="6ba9e854-0698-4f17-a529-a30a78579806"><p>The <b>WKSTA_INFO_1018</b> structure specifies details about
the state of the <a href="3acf0e02-9bbd-4ce0-a7a0-586bc72d3ef4#gt_09dbec39-5e75-4d9a-babf-1c9f1d499625" data-linktype="relative-path">SMB</a> <a href="3acf0e02-9bbd-4ce0-a7a0-586bc72d3ef4#gt_15c89cb5-6767-49e7-b461-66acaf6c06c8" data-linktype="relative-path">network redirector</a>.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _WKSTA_INFO_1018 {
   unsigned long wki1018_sess_timeout;
 } WKSTA_INFO_1018,
  *PWKSTA_INFO_1018,
  *LPWKSTA_INFO_1018;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>wki1018_sess_timeout:</b> The number of seconds
the <a href="3acf0e02-9bbd-4ce0-a7a0-586bc72d3ef4#gt_434b0234-e970-4e8c-bdfa-e16a30d96703" data-linktype="relative-path">server (2)</a> MUST wait
before disconnecting an inactive session.</p></div>